    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 11th level, your shouts can be heard by all.</p><p> Even when they can't, it still finds a way to reach them.</p><p> When a creature would be immune to Genjutsu with the auditory keyword, they instead have advantage on the saving throw.</p><p> If a creature would use a reaction against a Genjutsu with the Auditory Keyword that you cast, you may spend 4 Cursed Energy and ignore the effects of that reaction.</p><p></p>",
